Blend together 2 cups or 1 can of BACARDI(R) Mixers Pina Colada mix, 1/2 cup of BACARDI(R) Rum and 5 cups of ice for 45 to 60 seconds or until uniform. Add 7-10 drops of blue food coloring or Blue Curacao to taste. Blend and fill each cocktail glass 1/3 of the way full. Repeat step 1 using BACARDI(R) Mixers Pina Colada. (Without food coloring.) Repeat step 2 using BACARDI(R) Mixers Strawberry Daiquiri. Garnish with strawberries and serve immediately or freeze and serve for a tasty treat.